OL,3,CFree prom shop opens for young school
OL,4,Cpupils
OL,6,FA free prom shop has opened in
OL,7,FSalford, acting like a fairy godmother
OL,8,Fand make sure everyone has the chance
OL,9,Fto dress to impress on prom night.
OL,11,FThe shop in Walkden is designed to
OL,12,Fmake prom shopping more affordable,
OL,13,Fpassing on free dresses that have been
OL,14,Fdonated and would have cost hundreds
OL,15,Fof pounds.
OL,17,FBecky Marshall set up the service in
OL,18,Fher living room last year and has now
OL,19,Fjoined forces with community charity
OL,20,FSalford Step into Action.
