OL,6,FShe said: "There's no criteria, we
OL,7,Fdon't require parents to be on
OL,8,Fbenefits. We believe that every young
OL,9,Fperson should go to prom."
OL,11,FStudent Leona Retford used the service
OL,12,Flast year, and came back to encourage
OL,13,Fothers to come and get their dream
OL,14,Fdress for the big night.
OL,16,FShe said: "It's really heartwarming
OL,17,Fbecause when it gets close to prom
OL,18,Fthere is a pressure to find a dress
OL,19,Ffor hundreds of pounds.
