OL,6,F"When I found out about this place I
OL,7,Fwas dead happy and it relieved the
OL,8,Fpressure.
OL,10,FShe said the feeling of not going
OL,11,Fwould have been "gutting".
OL,13,FProm dresses are often worn for one
OL,14,Fnight, so Becky wants them to be put
OL,15,Fto use for other people, rather than
OL,16,Fbeing left in wardrobes.
